It was hard for me to do exercise consistently, until I decided to do just pushups everyday.

However, I wanted to share my training, be motivated by friends sharing theirs, and track everything.

And we already had a group chat!

An app-free and engaging way to register your workout

The Workout Bot is a chat bot.


After joining your group, it'll track the exercises you log onto the chat, provide shareable links to both individual and group-wide workout dashboards, allow the creation of challenges, and more.


Only one user has to pay for and activate the bot as described in the documentation. Afterwards, any group member can type right away +50 pushups to begin.

The code the bot runs on your server is open source on github and written in Haskell. Feature requests and bug reports should be added to the issue tracker. PRs are welcome too!


You can read more about how the bot works on the documentation page.
